            },
            {
                "comment": "he's an amazing professor. His office hours are extremely helpful. the worksheets are a must. you have to work hard, but the class is curved.",
                "difficulty_rating": 2,
                "quality_rating": 5
            },
            {
                "comment": "McCoy was awesome. Absolutely would have him for an organic course again. He gives a ton of material to help you prepare for exams (which is all the class is graded on), is really clear in lecture and helpful in office hours. Exams aren't unfair and test you on things you need to know, not obscure material.",
                "difficulty_rating": 3,
                "quality_rating": 5
            },
            {
